name: Dominic Howe
profile_summary: The user is a 32-year-old ambitious Software Developer working in the Technology industry. He stands at 6'0" and graduated from the University of California, Los Angeles. Originally from San Francisco, California, he is currently looking to date in Los Angeles. A multi-language speaker of English and Spanish, he places importance in values such as ambition, family, and independence. He enjoys hiking, coding, and photography, and is characterized by an INTJ MBTI personality type. Politically liberal and agnostic by religious beliefs, he aims for a long-term monogamous relationship. Being a man, he identifies himself with "He/Him/His" pronouns, is straight, and of White Caucasian ethnicity. He doesn't have children currently but wishes to have some in the future. A dog-lover with a Gemini star sign, he exercises actively, often drinks but neither smokes nor uses drugs or marijuana.
